<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="536" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,259,1689]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1627,1653]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[849,913,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">medi-</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[967,1076,1628,1653]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">processus</emphasis>
, referring to the median process of the transtilla.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
